Neßmersiel is about 5 kilometres northwest of Dornum. From 1867 to 1977, Neßmersiel belonged to Norden (Altkreis Norden). ==Other websites== *Homepage of the municipality Dornum *Reederei Baltrum Linie GmbH & Co.
